reviewText: If you seek a go-to for referencing current creepy cat people stereotypes, look here.
Very outdated. It got weird at the end talking about gay cockroaches.
My cat has eaten garlic chicken before and he's 14.
Please do not ever feed your cats garlic as the woman training cats for tv and movies suggests.  It is a poison to them! Just horrible.

There's some really cool stuff. Very informative, but also some silly kitty moments in there too. Totally going to try some of the Hollywood cat training techniques with my cat, Sir Hubert McFluffington.

To say this Amazing Cats is Amazing is an understatement.  I was truly blown away by the absolute fun I had watching this.  Not only was this entertaining, but I learned so much.  Huzah for Amazing Cats
I Love it the cats even enjoy watching.
